STATE of North Carolina
v.
Douglas PAGE, Jr. No. 135P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 6, 2006. Douglas Page, Jr., Pro Se. William P. Hart, Senior Deputy Attorney General, Edward W. Grannis, Jr., District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 13th day of March 2006 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Cumberland County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 6th day of April 2006."
